The end of an era is here! In this episode of the Major Issues Podcast, the hosts take flight as they break down the fourth and final season of Superman & Lois. From heart-pounding battles to emotional family moments, the series brought new depth to the Man of Steel and his iconic legacy. Tune in as we explore the highs, lows, and ultimate farewell to one of the most grounded superhero dramas ever. Whether you're Team Superman or just love a great story, this episode is for you!

